---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import NeonCard from "@/components/NeonCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Principles | harder.dev" description="Guiding principles for AI and agentic experimentation.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="muted">/principles</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Principles</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">A small control panel for exploring tomorrow's tools without abandoning solid engineering.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container grid grid-2">
      <NeonCard>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;">1) Chase novelty, keep architecture clear</h2>
        <p style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
          New AI capabilities arrive weekly; systems still need to be explainable, testable, and maintainable.
        </p>
      </NeonCard>
      <NeonCard>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;">2) Guardrails before autonomy</h2>
        <p style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
          Instrument traces, limits, approvals, and rollback paths before turning agents loose.
        </p>
      </NeonCard>
      <NeonCard>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;">3) Evidence beats hype</h2>
        <p style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
          Prefer measurable outcomes, benchmarked behavior, and repeatable evals over one-off demos.
        </p>
      </NeonCard>
      <NeonCard>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;">4) Fresh inputs, trusted origins</h2>
        <p style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
          Keep signals current automatically while restricting ingestion to reputable engineering sources.
        </p>
      </NeonCard>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
